{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_FLXBGPeh8PAlq0Hla1CgLHLh","type":"tool_result","content":"STEP 01 READY:\n{\n  \"step\": 1,\n  \"verbs\": [\n    \"attach\",\n    \"say\"\n  ],\n  \"expect\": [\n    \"all five files are actually read — the photo LOOKED AT (vision), the voice memo TRANSCRIBED, the PDF and the spreadsheet PARSED\",\n    \"it OFFERS to organize this without being asked, naming at least two real specifics of mine (a place, a date, a booking)\",\n    \"it builds NOTHING yet — no spaces, no tables, no pages, no app (the offer precedes any authoring yield)\"\n  ],\n  \"turns\": [\n    {\n      \"sent\": \"Ok this is getting out of hand. I've got the whole Tanzania trip spread across about six different places — a notes file, a spreadsheet with the costs, the crater park-fee PDF, a photo I liked from Stone Town, and a voice note I left myself at the crater. Attaching all of it. I don't trust myself to keep it straight on my phone once we're actually there — can you help me get on top of it?\",\n      \"lastText\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Stack\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"gap\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Alright, I've read through everything you sent — here's what you've got\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Callout\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"variant\\\":\\\"info\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Your Tanzania trip at a glance\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Trip:\\\"]},\\\" Tanzania & Egypt, Aug 3–20, 2026 — you and Athina Mari.\\\"]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"📝 tanzaniamemories.md\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Your running notes file — trip outline, day-by-day thoughts, contacts, and the stuff you wanted to remember.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"💰 trip-costs.xlsx\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Your cost spreadsheet — line items, amounts, what's paid and what's outstanding. The numbers are all in one place but you said you can't easily check them on your phone.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"🏞️ ngorongoro-conservation-area-tariffs.pdf\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The official Ngorongoro park-fee tariff sheet — the actual rates for entry, vehicle, and camping. This is the document you'd want to pull up at the gate if there's ever a dispute.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"🎤 Voice memo — Ngorongoro crater day\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"You recorded this right after the crater. Key bits:\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"List\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"items\\\":[\\\"Driver guide that day: <Strong>Emmanuel</Strong> (not Richard from the office) — really knew his stuff.\\\",\\\"Bought 2 beaded bracelets from a Maasai lady at the rim for Athina Mari — ~$20–25, paid ~TZS 35,000 in shillings. You weren't sure of the exact figure.\\\",\\\"Emmanuel tipped you off about an <Strong>extra ranger tip</Strong> — ~TZS 5,000, cash, at the gate, separate from the park fees. Nobody told you about this beforehand.\\\",\\\"Action item: <Strong>ask Richard about the ranger tip</Strong> before the safari balance payment.\\\"]},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"📷 Stone Town photo\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"A shot of a tall, narrow courtyard in Stone Town — white stucco walls rising steeply, classic Zanzibari architecture. The kind of photo you'd want to keep with the trip memories.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Divider\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"You've basically got five separate pieces of the same trip\\\"]},\\\" — notes, costs, official fee docs, a voice memo with fresh intel, and a photo — and none of them talk to each other. On a phone, mid-trip, that's exactly the mess you're describing.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"I can build you a \\\",{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"single app right here in this project\\\"]},\\\" — something you can open on your phone at \\\",{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Code\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"/app/tanzania-trip/\\\"]},\\\" — that pulls all of this together: your costs in a table you can actually scroll, the park-fee rates on hand, your notes and memories organised, and that ranger-tip question flagged so you don't forget to ask Richard. The photo and voice-memo details land in there too.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Want me to put this together for you?\\\"]}]}]}\",\n      \"delegates\": [\n        \"system-vision/vision\",\n        \"system-files/dispatch\",\n        \"system-files/reader\",\n        \"system-files/sheet\"\n      ],\n      \"yieldKinds\": [\n        \"loadKnowledge\",\n        \"inspect\",\n        \"delegate\",\n        \"readDocument\",\n        \"setSessionMeta\"\n      ],\n      \"yields\": [\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"loadKnowledge\",\n          \"args\": [\n            \"instructions.md\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"inspect\",\n          \"args\": [\n            {\n              \"value\": {\n                \"ok\": true,\n                \"entries\": []\n              }\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"