ngoro gate: ~TZS 5,000 cash, separate from park fees. This was not disclosed beforehand. Confirm with Richard at Suricata Safaris (+255 763 222 293) whether this is expected and if it should be budgeted. Ask BEFORE paying the $960 safari balance on arrival.\",\n1807\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1808\t          \"category\": \"payment\",\n1809\t          \"done\": false,\n1810\t          \"due_date\": \"Before Aug 7 (safari start)\"\n1811\t        },\n1812\t        {\n1813\t          \"id\": \"c5e45ca5-450e-4060-a3d4-6d907b112196\",\n1814\t          \"title\": \"Pay safari balance — $960 USD cash on arrival\",\n1815\t          \"detail\": \"Suricata Safaris balance: $960 total ($1,200 less $240 deposit). Must be paid in cash with post-2009 USD notes. Alternative: online via Pesapal (+5% surcharge = $1,008): payments.pesapal.com/suricatasafaris.\",\n1816\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1817\t          \"category\": \"payment\",\n1818\t          \"done\": false,\n1819\t          \"due_date\": \"Aug 7 (safari arrival)\"\n1820\t        },\n1821\t        {\n1822\t          \"id\": \"19d2d55e-57be-46fb-b2cd-7df3bf9c8cb2\",\n1823\t          \"title\": \"Apply for Tanzania e-visa (2 travelers × $50)\",\n1824\t          \"detail\": \"Mandatory online at visa.immigration.go.tz. Visa-on-arrival NO LONGER available as of January 2025. Apply well in advance. $100 total for both travelers.\",\n1825\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1826\t          \"category\": \"visa\",\n1827\t          \"done\": false,\n1828\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1829\t        },\n1830\t        {\n1831\t          \"id\": \"fd45fc33-3436-404f-a360-3ff85e933388\",\n1832\t          \"title\": \"Apply for Egypt e-visa, multiple-entry (2 travelers × $65)\",\n1833\t          \"detail\": \"Apply separately per traveler at the Egypt e-visa portal. Multiple-entry required. Printed copy MANDATORY — print and carry. $130 total.\",\n1834\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1835\t          \"category\": \"visa\",\n1836\t          \"done\": false,\n1837\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1838\t        },\n1839\t        {\n1840\t          \"id\": \"2b57e94c-9145-4e85-8297-4106aed5a595\",\n1841\t          \"title\": \"Get Zanzibar mandatory travel insurance from ZIC (2 travelers × $44)\",\n1842\t          \"detail\": \"Zanzibar Insurance Corporation travel insurance is MANDATORY for Zanzibar entry. $88 total for both travelers. Arrange before departure.\",\n1843\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1844\t          \"category\": \"visa\",\n1845\t          \"done\": false,\n1846\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1847\t        },\n1848\t        {\n1849\t          \"id\": \"55f4c833-3966-4e6b-a846-02e4edefaef6\",\n1850\t          \"title\": \"Arrange Zanzibar local driving permit (~$15)\",\n1851\t          \"detail\": \"Vasilis holds an IDP. A local Zanzibar Driving Permit is also required (~$15, valid up to 3 months). Most rental companies arrange with license photo provided 24+ hours before arrival. Police checkpoints are frequent — carry both IDP and local permit (screenshot acceptable).\",\n1852\t          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n1853\t          \"category\": \"transport\",\n1854\t          \"done\": false,\n1855\t          \"due_date\": \"24h before Zanzibar arrival (Aug 10-11)\"\n1856\t        },\n1857\t        {\n1858\t          \"id\": \"4404aa77-6b13-40cb-8c6d-a0709be2027f\",\n1859\t          \"title\": \"Pack warm layers for Ngorongoro\",\n1860\t          \"detail\": \"Ngorongoro nights are COLD. Bring warm layers — fleece, jacket, beanie. Evenings at Twiga Camp Site (Tarangire/Lake Manyara) also cool. Decathlon Forclaz trekking line recommended.\",\n1861\t          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n1862\t          \"category\": \"packing\",\n1863\t          \"done\": false,\n1864\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1865\t        },\n1866\t        {\n1867\t          \"id\": \"a3c9333c-2b16-4c8d-8758-7a0d9b84999d\",\n1868\t          \"title\": \"Pack DEET-based insect repellent\",\n1869\t          \"detail\": \"Essential for Tanzania safari and Zanzibar. DEET-based repellent strongly recommended.\",\n1870\t          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n1871\t          \"category\": \"packing\",\n1872\t          \"done\": false,\n1873\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1874\t        },\n1875\t        {\n1876\t          \"id\": \"43601ab7-0339-442b-9c74-fd0c82309fbf\",\n1877\t          \"title\": \"Use soft bags for Precision Air flights\",\n1878\t          \"detail\": \"Precision Air TC144 (DAR→ARK) and TC145 (ARK→ZNZ) have luggage restrictions favoring soft bags. Avoid hard-shell suitcases for these legs.\",\n1879\t          \"priority\": \"low\",\n1880\t          \"category\": \"packing\",\n1881\t          \"done\": false,\n1882\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1883\t        },\n1884\t        {\n1885\t          \"id\": \"7eef70fb-9d01-4f39-a3ba-1558b71f12af\",\n1886\t          \"title\": \"Print Egypt e-visa copies\",\n1887\t          \"detail\": \"Egypt e-visa requires a MANDATORY printed copy. Do not rely on digital only.\",\n1888\t          \"priority\": \"high\",\n1889\t          \"category\": \"visa\",\n1890\t          \"done\": false,\n1891\t          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n1892\t        },\n1893\t        {\n1894\t          \"id\": \"3d7bc74d-e278-4d58-b3b8-cf0da1d6bd5f\",\n1895\t          \"title\": \"The Rock Restaurant dinner — Aug 15, 18:00-20:00\",\n1896\t          \"detail\": \"Confirmed and fully paid ($46). 2 adults, 2x Tropical Passion Fruit Cheesecake. Outdoor seating for sunset/star views. Contact: +255 776 591 360 / +255 763 070 658.\",\n1897\t          \"priority\": \"low\",\n1898\t          \"category\": \"other\",\n1899\t          \"done\": false,\n1900\t          \"due_date\": \"Aug 15\"\n1901\t        },\n1902\t        {\n1903\t          \"id\": \"78f35091-9278-4303-9abf-265e5e164dd0\",\n1904\t          \"title\": \"Carry po