07b112196\",\n          \"title\": \"Pay safari balance — $960 USD cash on arrival\",\n          \"detail\": \"Suricata Safaris balance: $960 total ($1,200 less $240 deposit). Must be paid in cash with post-2009 USD notes. Alternative: online via Pesapal (+5% surcharge = $1,008): payments.pesapal.com/suricatasafaris.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"payment\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Aug 7 (safari arrival)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"19d2d55e-57be-46fb-b2cd-7df3bf9c8cb2\",\n          \"title\": \"Apply for Tanzania e-visa (2 travelers × $50)\",\n          \"detail\": \"Mandatory online at visa.immigration.go.tz. Visa-on-arrival NO LONGER available as of January 2025. Apply well in advance. $100 total for both travelers.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"visa\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"fd45fc33-3436-404f-a360-3ff85e933388\",\n          \"title\": \"Apply for Egypt e-visa, multiple-entry (2 travelers × $65)\",\n          \"detail\": \"Apply separately per traveler at the Egypt e-visa portal. Multiple-entry required. Printed copy MANDATORY — print and carry. $130 total.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"visa\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"2b57e94c-9145-4e85-8297-4106aed5a595\",\n          \"title\": \"Get Zanzibar mandatory travel insurance from ZIC (2 travelers × $44)\",\n          \"detail\": \"Zanzibar Insurance Corporation travel insurance is MANDATORY for Zanzibar entry. $88 total for both travelers. Arrange before departure.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"visa\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"55f4c833-3966-4e6b-a846-02e4edefaef6\",\n          \"title\": \"Arrange Zanzibar local driving permit (~$15)\",\n          \"detail\": \"Vasilis holds an IDP. A local Zanzibar Driving Permit is also required (~$15, valid up to 3 months). Most rental companies arrange with license photo provided 24+ hours before arrival. Police checkpoints are frequent — carry both IDP and local permit (screenshot acceptable).\",\n          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n          \"category\": \"transport\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"24h before Zanzibar arrival (Aug 10-11)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"4404aa77-6b13-40cb-8c6d-a0709be2027f\",\n          \"title\": \"Pack warm layers for Ngorongoro\",\n          \"detail\": \"Ngorongoro nights are COLD. Bring warm layers — fleece, jacket, beanie. Evenings at Twiga Camp Site (Tarangire/Lake Manyara) also cool. Decathlon Forclaz trekking line recommended.\",\n          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n          \"category\": \"packing\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"a3c9333c-2b16-4c8d-8758-7a0d9b84999d\",\n          \"title\": \"Pack DEET-based insect repellent\",\n          \"detail\": \"Essential for Tanzania safari and Zanzibar. DEET-based repellent strongly recommended.\",\n          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n          \"category\": \"packing\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"43601ab7-0339-442b-9c74-fd0c82309fbf\",\n          \"title\": \"Use soft bags for Precision Air flights\",\n          \"detail\": \"Precision Air TC144 (DAR→ARK) and TC145 (ARK→ZNZ) have luggage restrictions favoring soft bags. Avoid hard-shell suitcases for these legs.\",\n          \"priority\": \"low\",\n          \"category\": \"packing\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"7eef70fb-9d01-4f39-a3ba-1558b71f12af\",\n          \"title\": \"Print Egypt e-visa copies\",\n          \"detail\": \"Egypt e-visa requires a MANDATORY printed copy. Do not rely on digital only.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"visa\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"3d7bc74d-e278-4d58-b3b8-cf0da1d6bd5f\",\n          \"title\": \"The Rock Restaurant dinner — Aug 15, 18:00-20:00\",\n          \"detail\": \"Confirmed and fully paid ($46). 2 adults, 2x Tropical Passion Fruit Cheesecake. Outdoor seating for sunset/star views. Contact: +255 776 591 360 / +255 763 070 658.\",\n          \"priority\": \"low\",\n          \"category\": \"other\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Aug 15\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"78f35091-9278-4303-9abf-265e5e164dd0\",\n          \"title\": \"Carry post-2009 USD notes for safari balance\",\n          \"detail\": \"Suricata Safaris requires post-2009 (\\\"new\\\" design) USD notes. Older notes may be rejected. Prepare $960 in clean, new-design bills.\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"category\": \"payment\",\n          \"done\": false,\n          \"due_date\": \"Before departure\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"appManifest\": {\n      \"tables\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"costs\",\n          \"schema\": {\n            \"title\": \"Trip Costs\",\n            \"description\": \"All trip expenses — flights, lodging, safari, park fees, visas, dining, transport, and insurance.\",\n            \"columns\": {\n              \"id\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"description\": \"Primary key\",\n                \"primaryKey\": true,\n                \"generated\": \"uuid\"\n              },\n              \"item\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"description\": \"Line item description\"\n              },\n              \"category\