d you can't easily check them on your phone.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"🏞️ ngorongoro-conservation-area-tariffs.pdf\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The official Ngorongoro park-fee tariff sheet — the actual rates for entry, vehicle, and camping. This is the document you'd want to pull up at the gate if there's ever a dispute.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"🎤 Voice memo — Ngorongoro crater day\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"You recorded this right after the crater. Key bits:\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"List\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"items\\\":[\\\"Driver guide that day: <Strong>Emmanuel</Strong> (not Richard from the office) — really knew his stuff.\\\",\\\"Bought 2 beaded bracelets from a Maasai lady at the rim for Athina Mari — ~$20–25, paid ~TZS 35,000 in shillings. You weren't sure of the exact figure.\\\",\\\"Emmanuel tipped you off about an <Strong>extra ranger tip</Strong> — ~TZS 5,000, cash, at the gate, separate from the park fees. Nobody told you about this beforehand.\\\",\\\"Action item: <Strong>ask Richard about the ranger tip</Strong> before the safari balance payment.\\\"]},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"📷 Stone Town photo\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"A shot of a tall, narrow courtyard in Stone Town — white stucco walls rising steeply, classic Zanzibari architecture. The kind of photo you'd want to keep with the trip memories.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Divider\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"You've basically got five separate pieces of the same trip\\\"]},\\\" — notes, costs, official fee d