k fees — nobody told you about this beforehand.\\\",\\\"You need to ask Richard about the ranger tip before the safari balance payment.\\\"]},\\\"children\\\":[]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Divider\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Right now these five sources live in different places, and none of them talk to each other — a notes file, a spreadsheet, a PDF, a photo, and the memory in a voice note. When you're on your phone at the crater rim, that's not a filing system, it's a scavenger hunt.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Want me to put this all together into something you can actually open on your phone — a single Tanzania trip app here in this project, with your costs tracked, your itinerary readable, the park fees referenceable, and a place for the loose ends like the ranger tip and the bracelets? I'd pull every row from your spreadsheet, every detail from your notes, the photo, and the voice-memo specifics straight in.\\\"]}]}\",\n      \"delegates\": [\n        \"system-files/dispatch\",\n        \"system-vision/vision\",\n        \"system-files/reader\",\n        \"system-files/sheet\"\n      ],\n      \"yieldKinds\": [\n        \"delegate\",\n        \"loadKnowledge\",\n        \"readDocument\",\n        \"inspect\",\n        \"setSessionMeta\"\n      ],\n      \"yields\": [\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n          \"args\": \"[\\\"system-files\\\",\\\"dispatch\\\",null,{\\\"query\\\":\\\"Summarize these documents and list ALL concrete facts, names, dates, costs, locations, figures, and specifics from each one. The Markdown notes file, the Excel cost spreadsheet (sheet names and key columns/rows), and the Ngorongoro park-fee PDF — give me a concise summary per document plus the key specifics I need to speak accurately about this Tanzania tr…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n          \"args\": [\n  